### Get all books
GET http://localhost:3000/books

### Get book by id
GET http://localhost:3000/books/68d83f63b6e4b4e177484235

### Create book
POST http://localhost:3000/books HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "book_id": 2,
  "title": "1984",
  "author": "George Orwell",
  "genre": "Dystopian Fiction",
  "year_published": 1949,
  "isbn": "9780451524935",
  "available_copies": 5
}

### PUT book
PUT http://localhost:3000/books/68d83f63b6e4b4e177484235 HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "book_id": 1,
  "title": "To Kill a Mockingbird",
  "author": "Harper Lee",
  "genre": "Classic Fiction",
  "year_published": 1960,
  "isbn": "9780061120084",
  "available_copies": 5
}

